CoinDescription: It is a standard circulation coin for 25 Paise denomination. It was minted during the period of (2019-2020). It is a bimetallic coin ie Copper-Nickel-Zinc metal composition is in center with Copper-Nickel composition ring around it. It weights 8.65g with 27mm diameter and 2.15mm thickness. On heads, it features Ashoka Stambh with 'India' written around it in English and Hindi. On tails side we see denomination written at the centre.
